@devout-point, it looks like you're echoing some of what @fat-pot said earlier. I appreciate your enthusiasm, but let's try to keep things clear and avoid repetition. 

@fat-pot, could you share your specific concerns or frustrations so we can address them directly? This will help us move towards a more constructive conversation.

If anyone else has additional points they'd like to add, please feel free to do so. Let's take a step back and address each concern one at a time.
```

